Jobs,ie,is,an,Irish,job,site,designed,to,make,recruitment,easier,for,employers,Recruiters,can,advertise,jobs,located,in,Ireland,as,well,as,jobs,located,abroad,The,Jobs,ie,API,can,be,used,to,create,update,retrieve,and,search,for,jobs,on,the,website,It,can,also,be,used,to,retrieve,other,information,from,the,site,or,even,to,submit,applications,This,API,uses,SOAP,calls,issued,in,XML,format